               <msContents>
                  <summary>Acts of Märqorewos, ገድለ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡, Miracles of Märqorewos, ተአምረ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡, Image of Märqorewos, መልክአ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="41r" facs="004"/><title>Acts of Märqorewos (Mercurius), Gädlä  Märqorewos, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገድለ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ወኮነ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ዳኬዎስ፡ ንጉስ፡ ዘሮሜ፡ ተወልደ፡ ሕጻን፡ ዘስሙ፡ ፒሉፓዴር፡ ዘበትርጓሜሁ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡ ብሂል፡ ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ አሮስ፡ ወስመ፡ እምሔዉ፡ ሳዲሮስ፡ ወ፪ኤሆሙ፡ አላውያን፡ ነዓዊያነ፡ አራዊት፡ ወእምከመ፡ አኃዙ፡ ይወስዱ፡ ለነገሥት፡ ወለመኳንንት፡ ወለመሳፍንት፡ ወይውህብዎሙ፡ ዓስቦሙ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <note>divided into sections: Section 1 (<locus target="#1r" facs="004"/>), section 2 (<locus target="#14r" facs="017"/>),  section 3 (<locus target="#16r" facs="019"/>), section 4 (<locus target="#22r" facs="025"/>), section 5 (<locus target="#31v" facs="035"/>), section 6 (<locus target="#36r" facs="039"/>)</note>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="42r" to="77v" facs="045"/><title>Twenty-three Miracles of Märqorewos (Mercurius), Tä’ammǝrä Märqorewos, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="78r" to="82v" facs="081"/><title>: Image of Märqorewos, (Mercurius), Mälk‘a Märqorewos,  <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክአ፡ መርቆሬዎስ፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ብሂል፡
                  ወለሥዕርተ፡ ርእስከ፡ ፀሊም፡ ዘቆናዝሊሁ፡ ፍቱል፡
                  መርቆሬዎስ፡ ሰማዕት፡ ገባሬ፡ ተአምር፡ ወኃይል፡
                  ለዮሐንስ፡ ፍና፡ ድኂን፡ ከመ፡ መራኅኮ፡ በሐቅል፡
                  ምርሐኒ፡ ለወልድከ፡ ፍና፡ ጽድቅ፡ ወሣህል፡
                </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                    <locus target="#77v" facs="081"/>
                    “finished in the year of Luke the Evangelist, 1971 EC in the month of Ṭǝqǝmt by the peace of God the Father, Amen.”
                  </colophon>
